data.description: Step outside to your own private oasis equipped with extended cover patio + new pebble tec pool.  The large backyard (11,892sf) has fresh grass + space for all the activities. The possibilities are endless. No HOA. The home boasts tons of natural light, as you enter, + flows throughout the house. Kitchen features granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances, + eat in kitchen. Additional seating in front of the large bay window overlooks your stunning backyard + opens in to your large family room.Large primary suite with walk-in closet. Enjoy your neighborhood walks along the canal + park down the road. Close to shopping, restaurants, this is a home you won't want to miss.
